                <expan><abbr>Inv</abbr><ex>icto</ex></expan> Mit<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>r</abbr><ex>ae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Sa<supplied reason="lost">tur</supplied>ninus </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>onum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>edit</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Teller aus Terra Sigillata; mehrere Fragmente erhalten. Z. 1: geschrieben in einem Kreis; Z. 2: direkt ins Zentrum geschrieben. (B): AE 1998, Wiblé 1995: Z. 1: [Deo] Inv(icto) Mit(h)r(ae) C(aius) Cond[ius? ---]; Z. 2: [d(onum)] d(edit).</p>
            </div>
